= This Folder contains the TLM Module of the GPTimer =
== TLM Model ==
gptimer.h          - The GPTimer TLM Header
gptimer.cpp        - The GPTimer TLM Implementation
gpcounter.h        - Counter Class Header (A counter instance inside the Timer)
gpcounter.cpp      - Counter Class Implementation

== RTL Wrapper ==
tests/gptimer_warpper.vhd

== Tests ==
tests/testbench.h        - A generic LT Testbench to stimulate RTL and TLM Models

tests/functiontest.h
tests/registertest.h
tests/prescalertest.h

== Test Utils ==
tests/test.sh            - A script to automate a serie of Tests
tests/gptimertestbench.h - A generic testbench class for a GPTimer instance
tests/top.h              - A Headerfile which selects the Test
tests/top_LT.cpp         - The Top-Level-File for the TLM Model Test
tests/top_CT.cpp         - The Top-Level-File for the RTL Model Test

== Others ==
wscript                  - Build instructions for waf
README                   - This file

= How to build =
The best way to build it is to use the top-level waf build system:
>>> ./waf configure
>>> ./waf

